<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1>About me</h1>

    <hr>

    <div class="row">

      <div class="col-md-8">
        <p>I have started to learn web development and specifically Rails in late 2016. The decision came out of intereste to programming and to web development particularly. I went through several introductory course to decide that Ruby on Rails would be most suitable for my goals. Since then I have been studying in my free time and developing my skills through variety of courses and web apps.</p>
        <p> My github profile: <%= link_to "github.com/nlukjanov", "https://github.com/nlukjanov" %></p>
        <p>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#jobHistory"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-container="jobHistory"
          >
            Job History
          </button>

          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#education"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-container="education"
          >
            Education
          </button>
        </p>

        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Job 1
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Job 2
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Job 3
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Education 1
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Education 2
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Education 3
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "300x400.png", alt: "Profile Image", class: 'profile-img' %>
        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            <div class="skill">
              <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
              <div class="progress">
                <div
                  class="progress-bar progress-bar-stripped bg-warning"
                  role="progressbar"
                  aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                  aria-valuemax="100"
                  style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                  >
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>


